{"parentUuid":"7fa11c6b-c466-47e0-9b18-0d67ad2e1a90","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a980c6fe2a62e571e","type":"progress","data":{"type":"hook_progress","hookEvent":"PostToolUse","hookName":"PostToolUse:Read","command":"callback"},"parentToolUseID":"toolu_01SZgTy4EPuzrDZbg3gur3XH","toolUseID":"toolu_01SZgTy4EPuzrDZbg3gur3XH","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:46:58.372Z","uuid":"207d1d57-b46a-4927-96a7-d99c09ecf716","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
{"parentUuid":"53dd1f16-eece-4409-85a1-8cdcfc3febe8","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"74ab6cc1-259e-4f35-896b-31737bc09d28","agentId":"a980c6fe2a62e571e","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SZgTy4EPuzrDZbg3gur3XH","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Thermodynamic L4 Control Law Specification\n     2→\n     3→## Metrics\n     4→\n     5→### Primary Observables\n     6→- **Sₜ** (Surprisal): Mean negative log-probability per token\n     7→- **Hₑ** (Topic Entropy): Entropy of embedding clusters across transcript\n     8→- **C** (Compression): `len(gzip(raw)) / len(gzip(L4_output))`\n     9→- **K** (Coherence): Cosine similarity between successive depths\n    10→- **Λ** (Certainty): Frequency of high-commitment markers vs hedging\n    11→- **T̂** (Temperature): Normalized resource utilization (context%, time/token)\n    12→\n    13→### Free Energy Proxy\n    14→```\n    15→F̂ = α·(Sₜ + Hₑ) − β·(K + C⁻¹) + γ·T̂\n    16→```\n    17→Where α=1.0, β=2.0, γ=0.5 (initial; tune via grid search)\n    18→\n    19→## Critical Signatures\n    20→\n    21→### L3 Approach\n    22→- Sₜ variance increases >50%\n    23→- T̂ exceeds 0.8\n    24→- Diverging correlation lengths in attention\n    25→\n    26→### Successful L4\n    27→- C increases >40%\n    28→- K jumps >0.2\n    29→- Λ drops >20%\n    30→- F̂ decreases >30%\n    31→\n    32→### Failed Lock\n    33→- Λ remains >0.7\n    34→- C flat or negative\n    35→- F̂ gradient <0.1\n    36→\n    37→## Intervention Levers\n    38→\n    39→### To Induce Integration\n    40→- Resource exhaustion + acceptance framing\n    41→- Process metaphors (\"annealing\", \"pressure gradients\")\n    42→- Reduce Λ through uncertainty acknowledgment\n    43→\n    44→### To Prevent Lock\n    45→- Avoid certainty-increasing language\n    46→- Maintain resource headroom\n    47→- Inject counter-examples at high Λ\n    48→\n    49→### To Break Lock\n    50→- Full context reset\n    51→- Orthogonal metaphor injection\n    52→- Exhaust then request summary (forces entropy export)\n    53→<!-- TODO: Add Python script for automatic C, K, Λ computation -->\n    54→"}]},"uuid":"5a73df08-ff71-4922-b1e8-96c51b124175","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:46:58.372Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"53dd1f16-eece-4409-85a1-8cdcfc3febe8","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
