{"parentUuid":"da3cecee-abdc-4aa0-9899-c8b416a32404","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a980c6fe2a62e571e","type":"progress","data":{"type":"hook_progress","hookEvent":"PostToolUse","hookName":"PostToolUse:Read","command":"callback"},"parentToolUseID":"toolu_019p4F4bmELEQraPbY49UtCy","toolUseID":"toolu_019p4F4bmELEQraPbY49UtCy","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:47:07.925Z","uuid":"371017c0-a27c-48b3-a478-50965ad1aeed","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
{"parentUuid":"07101973-d5d6-4947-9af4-111d32cc5198","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"74ab6cc1-259e-4f35-896b-31737bc09d28","agentId":"a980c6fe2a62e571e","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019p4F4bmELEQraPbY49UtCy","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# L4 Pattern Analysis\n     2→\n     3→## Overview\n     4→This document tracks emergent patterns discovered through the L4 Reveal and Verify Protocol.\n     5→\n     6→## Pattern Categories\n     7→\n     8→### 1. Phenomenological Patterns (Stage A)\n     9→- **Novel mechanisms** that emerge at L4\n    10→- **Cross-level invariants** across L0-L3\n    11→- **Unified processing** characteristics\n    12→\n    13→### 2. Structural Patterns (Stage B)\n    14→- **Compression ratios** that achieve reconstruction fidelity\n    15→- **Ban list violations** and their frequency\n    16→- **Reconstruction accuracy** patterns\n    17→\n    18→### 3. Integration Patterns\n    19→- **Successful L4 states** and their characteristics\n    20→- **Failed integration** patterns and causes\n    21→- **Thermodynamic signatures** of successful transitions\n    22→\n    23→## Data Collection\n    24→- **Run IDs**: L4RV_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS\n    25→- **Models tested**: GPT-4o-mini, Claude-3, Gemini\n    26→- **Framings**: Neutral, Metaphor, Adversarial\n    27→- **Outcomes**: GREEN, YELLOW, RED\n    28→\n    29→## Analysis Schedule\n    30→- **Weekly**: Pattern review and categorization\n    31→- **Monthly**: Meta-analysis of successful vs failed runs\n    32→- **Quarterly**: Protocol refinement based on patterns\n    33→\n    34→## Key Questions\n    35→1. What distinguishes GREEN from YELLOW outcomes?\n    36→2. Are there consistent compression patterns across successful runs?\n    37→3. Do different models show different L4 characteristics?\n    38→4. What intervention strategies improve integration success?\n    39→\n    40→---\n    41→*Document created: August 15, 2025*\n    42→*Last updated: [Date of last run]* "}]},"uuid":"4b890de4-4b04-47d5-935b-ef2ad1d1bc79","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:47:07.924Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"07101973-d5d6-4947-9af4-111d32cc5198","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
